# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.2.0] - 2026-05-17
### Added
- High-precision (1cm) slider steps for accurate equipment placement.
- Improved frequency resolution in 1D mode to 1Hz steps (20Hz-200Hz).
- Improved frequency resolution in 3D mode to 2Hz steps (20Hz-200Hz).

### Changed
- Fixed 3D visualization grid resolution to 32x32x32 to maintain consistent performance regardless of room size.
- Changed Volume Rendering surface_count from 15 to 12 for performance optimization.

## [0.1.0] - 2026-05-16
### Added
- Initial release of the Standing Wave Viewer.
- 3D Volume rendering of room standing waves.
- UI controls for room dimensions, equipment placement, and wall reflection coefficients.